RPG Apartments in their letters suggests a rent increase of 15 to 38 percent.
A special door for new rentals was opened at the client centre on 18 November.
"It's been going on for a week, so it's just in the pipeline", the workers behind the barrier respond after a moment of hesitation when the client introduces himself as a journalist.
Deregulation and the former mines of the Baka is a hot topic.
