For non-slotted slats with 14 to 18 slats, latex or sandwich mattresses (e.g. a combination of latex and coconut) are appropriate, but you will always benefit from slats with more slats, 28 or more, where the slats in the thigh area are doubled and their stiffness can be regulated.
